Moreover, the owner of the club had been denounced by neighbours for disturbing the peace, whereas according to her statement the noise was not caused by the visitors to the disco but by the occupants of the house and especially by the guests of the parties organized there, which, according to the angry neighbours, had been getting longer and longer in recent weeks.
The manager of the nightclub explained that the harassment was so great that she agreed with the owner of the building not to pay rent for the last nine months.
